<div class="container mt-5 text-center">
    <img src="/images/logo.jpg" alt="College Logo" style="width: 120px;" class="mb-3">
    <h2 class="fw-bold">Think Nursing Career Think Jyoti</h2>
    <p class="text-muted fs-5">
        We offer a wide range of high-quality teaching and extra-curricular activities.
    </p>
    <p class="text-secondary">
        Nursing as a profession and discipline utilizes clinical competence,
        critical thinking, communication, teaching learning, professionalism, 
        and caring and cultural competency to solve individual and community health problems.
        It encompasses provision of promotive, preventive, curative and rehabilitative 
        aspects of care to people across the life span in a wide variety of 
        healthcare settings. KINS is a pioneer institute of nursing education under KIIT
        Deemed to be University, recognized by Indian Nursing Council (INC) & Odisha State 
        Nursing Council, since 2008. It has been contributing significantly towards quality 
        nursing education & service. It has been providing a lifetime opportunity for 
        successful career-oriented aspirants to gain expertise in the latest trends of 
        nursing care under the guidance of skilled professionals. 
        The College believes in providing nursing education based and built on scientific 
        principles, sound educational theory and clinically sound practice in order
         to prepare clinically excellent, professionally qualified nurses who will 
         work efficiently in all health care settings to meet the health needs of the society. The College promotes research in Nursing and Faculty Development.
    </p>
    <hr class="mx-auto" style="width: 80px; border: 2px solid orange;">
</div>

